{{Use dmy dates|date=February 2016}} {{Infobox company | logo = Centauri Production logo (2007).png | logo_caption = Centauri Production logo | name = Centauri Production | type = [[Subsidiary]] | parent = [[Bohemia Interactive]] | foundation = 2000 | location = [[Prague]], [[Czech Republic]] | industry = [[Game development]] | products = ''[[Memento Mori (video game)|Memento Mori]]'', ''[[Pound of Ground]]'', ''[[Evil Days of Luckless John]]'', ''[[Gooka: Mystery of Janatris]]'', ''[[Horké Léto 2]]'', ''[[Domestic Violence: Game Over]]'', ''[[Fairy Tale About Father Frost]]'' }}
The '''Centauri Production''' is a [[Czech Republic|Czech]] software house which focuses mainly on [[video game]]s. It is also active in the production of multimedia applications and presentations, of the software for film and animation studios, and of web pages and interfaces. Centauri Production is a member of IDEA Games. On 30 September 2010, Centauri Production was acquired by fellow IDEA Games member [[Bohemia Interactive]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idea-games.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=165&Itemid=2 |title=Support |publisher=Idea Games |date= |accessdate=15 August 2013}}</ref> Despite this acquisition, Bohemia Interactive promises that the acquired companies, including Centauri Production, will continue to operate individually.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bistudio.com/index.php/english/company/profile |title=Bohemia Interactive company profile |publisher=Bistudio.com |date= |accessdate=15 August 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130811154953/http://www.bistudio.com/index.php/english/company/profile |archivedate=11 August 2013 |df=dmy }}</ref>
==Technologies used== The '''CPAL3D''' is Centauri's in-house [[game engine]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.adventureclassicgaming.com/index.php/site/interviews/511/|title=Karel Matějka, Jan Hloušek, Mirek Papež|work=Adventure Classic Gaming|accessdate=28 May 2010}}</ref> It was used to create ''Memento Mori'' (2008), winner of the Best Adventure Story award for year 2008 at Adventure Archiv.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mementomori-game.com/ |title=Memento Mori |publisher=Mementomori-game.com |date= |accessdate=15 August 2013}}</ref>
