{{about|the theatre company|the structure in construction|Load-bearing wall}} {{multiple issues| {{notability|Companies|date=October 2012}} {{primary sources|date=October 2012}} }} '''Supporting Wall''' is an award-winning [[London]]-based [[theatre]] and [[The arts|general arts]] production, promotion and management company, founded in 2008 by producers Ben Monks and Will Young. The company's own productions have primarily focused on new writing and contemporary theatre, while management and publicity work has included projects across theatre, comedy, film, live music and dance.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.supportingwall.com/about_supportingwall.html |title=supporting wall |publisher=supporting wall |date= |accessdate=2012-10-27}}</ref>
